    • Field Detail

      • POSITION

        static final BitField POSITION
        This bit indicates whether the PointData field specifies relative or absolute locations. If set, each element in PointData specifies a location in the coordinate space that is relative to the location specified by the previous element in the array. In the case of the first element in PointData, a previous location at coordinates (0,0) is assumed. If clear, PointData specifies absolute locations according to the #isCompressed() flag. Note If this flag is set, the #isCompressed() flag (above) is undefined and MUST be ignored.
